Package ritzow.solomon.engine.util

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Exitable
    Instances of Exitable can be passed to the Synchronizer utility to wait until exited.
    Installable
    This interface should be implemented by objects which have a startup period before functioning normally.
    Transportable
    Instances of Transportable can be passed to ByteUtil.serialize to convert them into byte array packages containing the data from getBytes and header information such as class name and length of data.
    Updatable
    Instances of Updatable can be added to a ClientUpdateManager to be updated repeatedly at a rate set by the ClientUpdateManager
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ByteUtil
    Contains various utility methods for reading and writing primitive and non-primitive types from and to byte arrays.
    Utility
    Contains a number of static utility methods relating to various systems (matrix/random math, time, synchronization, hitboxes)

    Utility.MathUtility  
    Utility.Matrix  
    Utility.Synchronizer  
    Utility.Time
